Class HelpCommand

java.lang.Object

java.lang.Cloneable
public class HelpCommand
extends Command

HELP command is responsible for showing the help. It delegates in the Parser in order to show the information help because it knows which are all the commands that the game is capable for executing.

Description copied from class: Command
Tries to configure the command with the information contained in a string.

Specified by:
parse in class Command
Parameters:
line - A string with the information for configuring the command
Returns:
  • False, if this command does not know how to parse the line or if the line contains mistakes and the command cannot be configured correctly.
  • True, otherwise. In this case, the command is correctly configured and ready to be executed
